# Agent Status Reports

When you finish a round of work, write your summary to:

```
plans/agent{N}-round{R}-report.md
```

For example, Agent 3 finishing Round 7 writes to `plans/agent3-round7-report.md`.

Include:
- Holes before/after per file (table format)
- Chapters closed
- Verification counts (verified, errors, RTT, PTT)
- Techniques used
- Remaining holes with brief explanation of what blocks them
- Commit hash on your branch
